- Workday is an on-demand (cloud-based) financial management and human capital management software vendor. 
- Founded by David Duffield - founder and former CEO of the ERP company PeopleSoft

Wokday HCM : It is a cloud-based human capital management software system that unifies a wide range of HR dunctionality into a single system.
             The software provides bebefits, talent management, payroll, time tracking, compensation, workforce panning and recruiting, finacial management.
